{"tid":1477794,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港銀行同業拆息(Hibor)普遍上升","createTime":"2019-08-16T08:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T14:20:13.000Z","uid":83654,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"007ab26ca4a74b99a4b1d91b54b0b1831fee3d86","tid":1477794,"uid":83654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"港元拆息︰1個月期升至2.26厘<br />\n<br />\n香港銀行公會公布香港銀行同業拆息(Hibor)普遍上升，隔夜息升至1.96厘，為7月9日以來高位；1星期及2星期拆息齊升破2厘水平；與樓按相關的1個月期拆息連升4日，至2.26厘；3個月期報2.38厘。<br />\n<br />\n16/8/2019<br />\n隔夜 1.96714厘<br />\n1星期 2.07750厘<br />\n2星期 2.17429厘<br />\n1個月 2.26286厘<br />\n2個月 2.35607厘<br />\n3個月 2.38375厘<br />\n6個月 2.38536厘<br />\n12個月 2.41375厘<br />\n<br />\n15/8/2019<br />\n隔夜 1.20000厘<br />\n1星期 1.71857厘<br />\n2星期 1.88228厘<br />\n1個月 2.14286厘<br />\n2個月 2.30071厘<br />\n3個月 2.35000厘<br />\n6個月 2.36054厘<br />\n12個月 2.43250厘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190816/bkn-20190816111854936-0816_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190816%2Fbkn-20190816111854936-0816_00842_001.html&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=b5801682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190816/bkn-20190816111854936-0816_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d782eb04d82627fa9580778f34304e07b5b4f1e3","tid":1477794,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:55:43.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2nDsML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2nDsML.jpg&h=4c89349c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZua3j6.jpg\" data-thumbnai